Cycling Game:

- individual racer until you reach a certain overall rating then you can qualify to be picked up by a team
- you play the game as an individual rider
- races auto-gen "open-racers" but at the start of game, pro teams are made and generated with a team of riders

- objects and their functionality
	- Rider
		- name
		- age
		- country
		- height
		- weight
		- bike
		- rating (1-10)
			- mtn rating
			- hill rating
			- flat rating
			- time trial rating
		- speed (mph)
			- mtn speed
			- hill speed
			- flat speed
			- time trial speed
		- Generator Functions
			- name
			- age
			- country
			- height
			- weight
			- bike
			- ratings
			- rider
	- Bike
		- name
		- rating
			- mtn rating
			- hill rating
			- flat rating
			- time trial rating
		- functions
			- generate name (make and model)
			- generate ratings
	- Team
		- name
		- country
		- team bike
		- riders<Rider>(20)
	- Obstacle
		- type
			- mtn -- avg spd: 20 to 25 mph (5mph/10ratings=0.5 difference for each rating)
			- hill -- avg spd: 23 to 26 mph (3mph/10ratings=0.3 difference for each rating)
			- flat -- avg spd: 25 to 28 mph (3mph/10ratings=0.3 difference for each rating)
			- tt -- avg spd: 29 to 31 mph  (2mph/10ratings=0.2 difference for each rating)
		- distance
			- mile marker of the course the obstacle starts
			- mile marker of the course the obstacle ends
		- points available for finishing the obstacle in top 3
		- functionality
			- would like to auto-gen an obstacle based on its type
	- Course
		- name
		- country
		- distance
		- obstacels<obstacle>() (this will be the profile of the course)
		- Generator Functions
			- country
			- distance
			- course
		- Other Functionality
			- adding adn removing obstacles
	- Event (can be 1 course or a series of courses called a Tour)
		- name
		- start date
		- end date
		- courses<course>
		- teams<team>
		- Generator Functions
			- riders
			- teams
			- course
			- tour (multiple courses)
		- Other Functionality
			- adding and removing a custom course
			- adding and removing a team
			- adding and removing a rider
			- start the race for all racers
			- scoring
				- Climber's Jersey: top 3 finishers get points
				- Sprinter's Jersey: top 3 finishers get points
				- Leader's Jersey: top 3 finishers get points


